# GM-3: Modular Enforcement
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All task orchestration

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Modular Enforcement: Loading and applying only the rules relevant to the current task or skill.

ENFORCE: Only rule subsets relevant to the current task may be loaded; log which subsets were loaded per task.
PROHIBIT: Loading all rules globally for every task.
ON VIOLATION: Halt execution if relevant rules fail to load → notify system administrator.
